data.title: GONE
data.text: Sorry if you actually hoped to find this place. It was basically the outdoor patio of Stick & Stein, a sports bar/pool hall type of place which served pretty good food (for a sports bar). Anyway, the whole establishment closed up, including all the businesses owned by Stick & Stein - Dade Country Jail, Martini Bar, and Fat Monkey's.

data.title: Simple to hang out.
data.text: Love this place, music is great.  DJ Cassy will play any song if you request.  Simple to hang out.  It is outdoors so, dress for the weather.  If it is not your seen There is Three other bars to choose from just pick your door.
